    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "grpc does work with ruby 2.0.0, but the application needs to pin dependencies on its own.\r\n\r\nHere is an example of that: https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/test/distrib/ruby/distribtest.gemspec\r\n\r\nThe problem here is just that grpc doesn't pin it's dependency on `jwt`.... and so `gem install grpc` attempts to grab the latest available version of `jwt` and then fails.\r\n\r\n"
